<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>rby̱ wʿwdk swr lḥyạty</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- rby̱ wʿwdk swr lḥyạty
 tḥmy ạlqlb mn ạlạ̉zmạt
 wʿd byḍmn ʿmry ạlậty
 wwʿd bfrḥ fy wsṭ ḍyqạt

[V2]
 ạlqrạr: wqt mạ ạ̉ỷn fy̱ wsṭ ậlạm
 tyjy tḥn wtʿṭy̱ slạm
 wtqwl ạ̹n ạlwʿd ḥạmyk
 ạ̹ny mʿạk kl ạlạ̉yạm

[V3]
 2- ḥbk lỹ̱ bysẖbʿ nfsy
 wyhwn kl ạlṣʿwbạt
 yrfʿ rwḥy̱ wybʿd yạ̉sy
 wbyskb fy ạlqlb tẖbạt

[V4]
 3- jwdk lỹ dạ ạ̉ʿẓm jwd
 ṭwl ạlʿmr rạḥ ạ̉sẖbʿ byh
 jwdk rḥmẗ wkẖyr mmdwd
 wqt mạ bạṭlb rạḥ ạlạqyh

[V5]
 4- wyạ ḥnạnk bạḥyạ sʿyd
 ykfy̱ ạlqlb ạ̹n ạ̉nạ wyạk
 lyl byfwt mʿ ṣbḥ jdyd
 yjy wạ̉htf ạ̹ny̱ mʿạk</lyrics>
<author>qs ạ̉mjd sʿd, hạny ạ̉nys</author>
<hymn_number>4366</hymn_number>
</song>